# Work Groups

When asked to show work groups, work chunks, or tagged task groupings:

1. Read `tasks/79-work-chunks.md` to get the current list of work chunk tags (listed under "Active work chunks" as bold tag names).
2. For each tag, search all `tasks/*.md` files for that tag in the `tags:` frontmatter line.
3. For each matching task, extract the `id` and `title` from frontmatter.
4. Present results as a table per tag:

```
### <tag-name>
| Task | Title |
|------|-------|
| <id> | <title> |
```

Only include tasks where the tag appears in the `tags:` frontmatter array. Exclude tasks with `status: completed` or `status: cancelled`. Exclude the work chunks task itself (task 79) from the results.
